<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - Panel Admin API Keys</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-bg: #000000;
            --secondary-bg: #1a1a1a;
            --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
            --accent-cyan: #06b6d4;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #a1a1aa;
            --border-color: #374151;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-bg) 0%, var(--secondary-bg) 100%);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .login-container {
            background: var(--secondary-bg);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-purple);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .login-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .login-header h2 {
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .login-header p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            background: var(--primary-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            background: var(--primary-bg);
            border-color: var(--accent-purple);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-login {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-purple) 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .btn-login:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, var(--accent-purple) 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .alert {
            background: var(--primary-bg);
            border: 1px solid #ef4444;
            color: #ef4444;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        
        .input-group-text {
            background: var(--primary-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;
        }
        
        .input-group .form-control {
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
        }
        
        .brand-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .footer-text a {
            color: var(--accent-purple);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer-text a:hover {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-header">
            <div class="brand-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h2>WolfData Admin</h2>
            <p>Panel de Administración API Keys</p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2"></i>
                <%= error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <form method="POST" action="/login">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="username" class="form-label">
                    <i class="fas fa-user me-2"></i>
                    Usuario
                </label>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-text">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                    </span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mb-4">
                <label for="password" class="form-label">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock me-2"></i>
                    Contraseña
                </label>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <span class="input-group-text">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    </span>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-login">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>
                Iniciar Sesión
            </button>
        </form>
        
        <div class="footer-text">
            <p>Desarrollado por <a href="https://t.me/zGatoO" target="_blank">@zGatoO</a></p>
            <p>Soporte: <a href="https://t.me/choco_tete" target="_blank">@choco_tete</a> | <a href="https://t.me/WinniePoohOFC" target="_blank">@WinniePoohOFC</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
